## Technology Stack

| Component | Technology |
|-----------|-----------|
| Language | Java 11 |
| REST Framework | JAX-RS (Jakarta RESTful Web Services) |
| Implementation | Jersey 3.1.3 |
| Server | Apache Tomcat 11 |
| Build Tool | Maven |
| Data Storage | ConcurrentHashMap (in-memory) |
| JSON Processing | Jackson (via jersey-media-json-jackson) |
| IDE | NetBeans |

