## Project Structure

```
src/main/java/com/smartcampus/smartcampusapi/
│
├── AppConfig.java                                 ← @ApplicationPath("/api/v1")
├── DataStore.java                                 ← In-memory ConcurrentHashMap storage
│
└── resources/
    ├── Room.java                                  ← Room POJO/DTO
    ├── Sensor.java                                ← Sensor POJO/DTO
    ├── SensorReading.java                         ← SensorReading POJO/DTO
    │
    ├── DiscoveryResource.java                     ← GET /api/v1
    ├── RoomResource.java                          ← /api/v1/rooms
    ├── SensorResource.java                        ← /api/v1/sensors
    ├── SensorReadingResource.java                 ← Sub-resource (no @Path)
    │
    ├── RoomNotEmptyException.java                 ← Custom exception
    ├── RoomNotEmptyExceptionMapper.java           ← Maps to 409 Conflict
    ├── LinkedResourceNotFoundException.java       ← Custom exception
    ├── LinkedResourceNotFoundExceptionMapper.java ← Maps to 422
    ├── SensorUnavailableException.java            ← Custom exception
    ├── SensorUnavailableExceptionMapper.java      ← Maps to 403 Forbidden
    ├── GlobalExceptionMapper.java                 ← Catch-all 500
    │
    └── LoggingFilter.java                         ← Request + Response logging

src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/
└── web.xml                                        ← Jersey servlet registration
```

